msgid "Controllers, gamepads, and joysticks"
msgstr "Controles, gamepads y joysticks"

msgid ""
"Godot supports hundreds of controller models thanks to the community-sourced "
"`SDL game controller database <https://github.com/gabomdq/"
"SDL_GameControllerDB>`__."
msgstr ""
"Godot admite cientos de modelos de controles gracias a la comunidad `SDL "
"game controller database <https://github.com/gabomdq/"
"SDL_GameControllerDB>`__."

msgid ""
"Controllers are supported on Windows, macOS, Linux, Android, iOS, and HTML5."
msgstr ""
"Los controles son compatibles con Windows, macOS, Linux, Android, iOS y "
"HTML5."

msgid ""
"Note that more specialized devices such as steering wheels, rudder pedals "
"and `HOTAS <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HOTAS>`__ are less tested and may "
"not always work as expected. Overriding force feedback for those devices is "
"also not implemented yet. If you have access to one of those devices, don't "
"hesitate to `report bugs on GitHub <https://github.com/godotengine/godot/"
"blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#reporting-bugs>`__."
msgstr ""
"Ten en cuenta que dispositivos más especializados como volantes, pedales de "
"timón y `HOTAS <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HOTAS>`__ (Hands-On Throttle "
"and Stick) son menos probados y es posible que no siempre funcionen como se "
"espera. La capacidad de anular la retroalimentación de fuerza para esos "
"dispositivos aún no está implementada. Si tienes acceso a alguno de esos "
"dispositivos, no dudes en `informar errores en GitHub <https://github.com/"
"godotengine/godot/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#reporting-bugs>`__."

msgid "In this guide, you will learn:"
msgstr "En esta guía aprenderás:"

msgid ""
"**How to write your input logic to support both keyboard and controller "
"inputs.**"
msgstr ""
"**Cómo escribir su lógica de entrada para admitir entradas de teclado y de "
"controles.**"

msgid "**How controllers can behave differently from keyboard/mouse input.**"
msgstr ""
"**Cómo los controles pueden comportarse de manera diferente a la entrada del "
"teclado/mouse.**"

msgid "**Troubleshooting issues with controllers in Godot.**"
msgstr "**Solución de problemas con los controles en Godot.**"

msgid "Supporting universal input"
msgstr "Soporte para entrada universal"

msgid ""
"Thanks to Godot's input action system, Godot makes it possible to support "
"both keyboard and controller input without having to write separate code "
"paths. Instead of hardcoding keys or controller buttons in your scripts, you "
"should create *input actions* in the Project Settings which will then refer "
"to specified key and controller inputs."
msgstr ""
"Gracias al sistema de acción de entrada de Godot, hace posible admitir la "
"entrada tanto del teclado como del control sin tener que escribir rutas de "
"código separadas. En lugar de codificar las teclas o los botones del control "
"en sus scripts, debe crear *acciones de entrada* en la Configuración del "
"Proyecto, que luego se referirán a las entradas de clave y control "
"especificadas."

msgid ""
"Input actions are explained in detail on the :ref:`doc_inputevent` page."
msgstr ""
"Las acciones de entrada se explican en detalle en la página :ref:"
"`doc_inputevent`."

msgid ""
"Unlike keyboard input, supporting both mouse and controller input for an "
"action (such as looking around in a first-person game) will require "
"different code paths since these have to be handled separately."
msgstr ""
"A diferencia de la entrada del teclado, admitir la entrada del mouse y del "
"control para una acción (como mirar alrededor en un juego en primera "
"persona) requerirá diferentes rutas de código, ya que deben manejarse por "
"separado."

msgid "Which Input singleton method should I use?"
msgstr "¿Qué método de entrada singleton debo usar?"

