"When you have two axes (such as joystick or WASD movement) and want both "
"axes to behave as a single input, use ``Input.get_vector()``:"
msgstr ""
"Cuando tenga dos ejes (como un joystick o movimiento WASD) y desee que ambos "
"ejes se comporten como una sola entrada, use ``Input.get_vector()``:"

msgid ""
"When you have one axis that can go both ways (such as a throttle on a flight "
"stick), or when you want to handle separate axes individually, use ``Input."
"get_axis()``:"
msgstr ""
"Cuando tiene un eje que puede ir en ambos sentidos (como un acelerador en "
"una palanca de vuelo), o cuando desea manejar ejes separados "
"individualmente, use ``Input.get_axis()``:"

msgid ""
"For other types of analog input, such as handling a trigger or handling one "
"direction at a time, use ``Input.get_action_strength()``:"
msgstr ""
"Para otros tipos de entrada analógica, como manejar un disparador o manejar "
"una dirección a la vez, use ``Input.get_action_strength()``:"

